		"description": "<p><em>Passive: You gain immunity to the grappled and restrained conditions unless you choose to accept them.</em></p><p><em><strong>Legend Dice Feature</strong></em><strong> — Liberating Strike:</strong> When you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you may expend a Legend Die to cause one creature of your choice (other than you) within 15 feet to immediately end one condition affecting it (except unconscious or doomed). You choose which condition ends.</p>",
